metadata.name: In Bloom
metadata.description: The flowers appear to be in full bloom, their petals soft and delicate, with a slight breeze causing them to gently sway. The girl is dressed in a simple,  white top that seems to complement the beauty of the flowers around her. The sunlight casts a warm glow across her face, highlighting her natural beauty and making her stand out even more against the dreamy, ethereal background of the garden.
